room_title: Escape room "Framed! The Art Heist" by Masterpiece Escapes in Charlotte
room_address: 14015 E Independence Blvd Indian Trail, NC 28079
room_description: The Paper Street Gallery is currently holding a rare artifact worth millions of dollars. A shipping error has caused this priceless artifact to arrive before the full security detail is set in place. You have a small window to relieve them of this artifact, but you will have to do so under the watchful eye of a diligent security guard.
